Dialogs.Dialog: Geez, don't be messing with me, okay?
Do you think I should forgive you?
Today is my birthday so, stay with me, okay?
Thank you for coming for my birthday.
What kind of person forgets his girlfriend's birthday?
Happy birthday, thank you for being born... I love you.
Happy birthday. I would really like if we could stay together.
Happy birthday! Today is the day when my most important person was born. I love you▼
Happy birthday, I wanted to congratulate you today...
Happy birthday. It's a little late, but...
Happy birthday! I hope I can say that to you next year too.
Today is the anniversary of when we first met. It's an important day for both of us.
Today is our anniversary... the first day I met you. Let's stay together forever.
What day is today?... The correct answer is the day we met. It's our anniversary.
Today is the day we started dating. I love you. More than before.
Today is the anniversary of our relationship. I love you. From now on, I'll always be there for you.
Today is the day we started dating. Did you remember it? Fufu, I love you▼
Today is the day we kissed for the first time. Do you want to remember it once more? *kiss*.
Today is... The anniversary of when you kissed me for the first time. So... *kiss*.
Do you know what kind of anniversary is today? The correct answer is... Can you come closer? ...*kiss*.
Hurry up, Monday. We shall do our best this week! Right?
It's Tuesday. We still have a lot of days before us, don't we? Do your best!
Wednesday. The turning point of the week, cheer up!
Thursday. What are your plans for the weekend... What do you want to do?
It's Friday. Isn't it a bit exciting?
It's Saturday! Hey, what should we do?
Finally, Sunday. Do you want to go out today?
I want to relax together on Sunday... Can we?
This wind is getting better and better.
Don't you want to take a walk when the weather is nice?
It's summer. We must do a lot of memories this year too, okay?
Every day it's too hot... Don't hurt you body okay?
Autumn... I'm feeling a little bit sentimental.
Autumn... The season when the potatoes are delicious... I'm kidding.
It's cold every day, isn't it?... Don't catch a cold now, okay?
Don't just curl up inside the kotatsu. Don't you want to go out together?
Happy New Year. Let's be together a lot more this year, okay?
I had my first dream... What kind of dream it was is a secret. Fufu.
My first dream was... I dreamed of you, and... It's embarrassing.
Did you have your first dream? Was I... in you dream? I'm kidding.
The new semester starts today. Let's do our best together!
I wonder if I can prepare Nanakusa porridge this year.
Today is the Coming-of-Age Day. I'd like to have an adult ceremony together.
It's the mirror opening today. Don't eat too much mochi, okay?
Today is Setsubun. I prepared some beans... Can I throw them?
Tachiharu. It's spring from today on the calendar, but real spring is still a long way off.
Today is the National Foundation Day. Do you know from where it comes?
What day is it today? ...Fufu, come on!
Today is a special day, so it's mine to have. Fufu!
February 14... What day is it? I'm kidding, fufu!
Leap years make you feel like you're a day older?
Spring is coming soon, the season of plum blossoms is about to come.
Today is a girl's only festival. Boys aren't allowed. Fufu, that's a lie.
Today is March 14th... No? Is that's all? Fufu!
I'm going to keep you all for myself today. Because it's March 14th.
Today is March 14th... That's is why you should stay only with me, okay?
In spring equinox, the day and night have the same length. Do you want to measure it? I'm kidding.
Spring break is coming soon. Let's make a lot of new friends this days, okay?
Spring break starts today. I don't have much homework to do, so let's spend time together.
I have never told a lie... Would you believe me if I say that?
You know, Manaka is actually a rabbit... it’s true!
I hate you... It's a lie! A lie! I'm sorry!
The new semester starts from today. Can we meet at school everyday?
I love cherry blossoms. Shall we go see them together?
Today is Showa Day. Emperor Showa's Birthday.
Golden Week is coming soon. Hey, where should we go?
Today is the Constitution Day. Do you want to be with me on the consecutive holidays?
Today is Green Day. Shall we go to a fresh green park?
Today is Children's Day. Hey, are we still children?
Tachi-Natsu. Today the calendar marks the beginning of summer.
Have you prepared a present for Mother's Day? When you give it, don't forget to say thanks.
It's sports festival today. Alright, I'll win all the events! I'm kidding.
Today is the longest day. Summer is approaching.
It's time to change clothes. When the rainy season is over, summer is already here.
Papa get's embarrassed in Father's Day. But I think he'll be happy if I give him a present.
It's sea day, but is the water still cold?
It's Tanabata. I want to write a request together on a bamboo strip...
After our tests are over, summer vacation is coming soon, right?
It's sea day, do you want to go out?
Summer vacation starts today! Let's make a lot of memories, okay?
Autumn starts today. It's still in the middle of summer outside, isn't it?
I like fireworks... We should see them together.
Today is Obon festival. Your ancestors are coming back, right?... That's a little scary, isn't it?
Summer vacation is over... But, can we meet again at school?
It's a cluster amaryllis. I wonder if I can make some Ohagi with it.
Respect-for-the-Aged Day. I gave a shoulder-massage ticket to my grandpa and grandma, it's was so nostalgic.
It's the Autumn equinox today. Have you noticed that the sky is a little higher recently?
It's about time to say goodbye to summer clothes. I hope they take care of me next year.
It's almost time for the moon of mid-autumn. Wouldn't it be nice to see a clear night sky and a beautiful moon?
Today is Halloween. Are you going to play me a trick? Fufu!
Today is Culture Day. I wonder what the culture is... I'm kidding, I know it.
It's getting pretty cold in the mornings and evenings. Will this winter be cold?
Shichigosan it's so nostalgic. I still have pictures on display in my house.
Labor Thanksgiving Day. What kind of work will we do in the future?
The School Festival is today. Fufu, the festival is very exciting.
Winter vacation is early this year.
Today is the Emperor's birthday, but it's Eve's day for us.
It's winter vacation... The year is coming to an end.
Merry Christmas. I want to thank God for meeting you.
Merry Christmas. May happiness comes to you again next year...
Merry Christmas. It would be nice if we could spend some time together...
It's already New Year's Eve... Thank you for taking care of me this year.
In a test don't be impatient, do it at your own pace, okay?
Long time no see... I was feeling lonely.
Don't forget about me anymore! Okay?
Ah... You finally arrived. Fufu, hurry up!
I'm so glad... I thought you forgot about me. Hey, did you hurry just for me?
Let's leave it at that. Fufu, did you come early just for me?
I'm glad to see you, but... don't get too fixed on it, okay?
You came again... I'm happy, but please take a break, okay?
Do you want to meet me so much? Fufu, are you sure it's okay?
Hello? You come to see me again.
Hey, are you sure it's not a coincidence?
Did you come to see me?
Hey... Did you come to visit me today?
Me, right? If it's you, then yes.
Hey, what are we doing today? Fufu!
Ah... I just wanted to see you. Fufu.
If I can't see you, then I'll just think about you.
I want you to know more about me...
I want you to teach me a lot of things I don't know.
Hey, did you come early just for me?
I just want to see you... Fufu, it was telepathy, right?
Do you want to stay together today?
Lately, I've been thinking a lot about you...
I want to know more about you...
Even if I can see you every day, it's not enough.
Where are you going to take me today?
You're so slow. Geez... Come on, don't you want to hurry?
And I was just thinking that I wanted to see you.
We must make memories together today, don't we?
I finally got to see you. I'm not going home anymore... I'm kidding.
I will tell you a lot of things you don't know... I'm kidding.
If we are together, each day is a special day, isn't it?
